<p>I published a new essay on philosophy: <a href="https://protesilaos.com/ecosystem-definitions-problems/">Ecosystem: definitions and
problems</a>. It tackles the idea of an
ecosystem as one of “universal interconnectedness”, examining the
problems that arise from it.</p>

<p>As with all publications on <a href="/">my website</a>, <em>Ecosystem: definitions and
problems</em> is distributed free of charge and freed from traditional
copyright restrictions, under the terms of the <em>Creative Commons
Attribution-ShareAlike Licence (CC BY SA) 4.0</em>.</p>

<p>For any further information, or to share your thoughts on this work,
feel welcome to <a href="https://protesilaos.com/contact/">contact me</a>.</p>